title: MBMBaM 376: Face 2 Face: Shrimp, Heaven, Live!
description: Here's our star-studded live show from the gorgeous King's Theater in Brooklyn, NY! We still cannot believe they allowed us to do a show there. It was irresponsible, is what it was.
author: shows@mbmbam.com (Justin McElroy)
